0.1.2 <2016-06-20>
------------------
- change signature on ``create_repo_from_pip_url`` to accept
  ``pip_url`` insetad of ``url``.
- ``Base`` to accept ``repo_dir`` instead of ``name`` and
  ``parent_dir``.

0.1.1 <2016-06-20>
------------------
